 <p><strong><a href="mailto:kezzek@thesafehouse.org"><font size="3" color="#A0B0E0">J.S. "Kezzek" Omundson</font></a><br><font size="2" color="yellow">Asst. Admin -</font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org"><font size="2" color="yellow"><i>TheSafehouse.org</i></font></a><br><font size="1" color="yellow"><u>email: </u></font><a href="mailto:kezzek@thesafehouse.org"><font size="1" color="yellow"><u>kezzek@thesafehouse.org</u></font></a><br><br><font size="2" color="#A0B0E0"><i>Someone set us up the YOLG !!</i></font></a></strong></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukoru.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Koru</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/10/01 11:37:29 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Save a good EQ website</span><hr size=1> Are many of you planing on signing up for this? I'm sincerely interested in seeing if many of you feel it is important enough to you to pay for it.<br>
